    • Field Detail

      • SAFE_HEAP_SIZE

        public static final long SAFE_HEAP_SIZE
        the safe heap size allocated to use if it is more than this we will use oat2dex as library rather than a binary if it is less than this we will call oat2dex as binary with specific heap size set by the user him self this is the only way to avoid OutofMemory exception because I can't determine the host available ram memory and I can't change heap size after Launch and not all users know the -Xmx JVM arg so lets do it for them
